title: CSE: 2015-1005 - New Listing - DGS Minerals Inc. (DLE)
text:
October 15, 2015 15:36 ET CSE: 2015-1005 - New Listing - DGS Minerals Inc. (DLE) 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - Oct. 15, 2015) - The common shares of DGS Minerals Inc. have been approved for listing on the CSE. 
Listing and disclosure documents will be available at thecse.com Trading Date: October 16, 2015 Symbol: DLE ISIN: CA 23290K 20 5 6 Boardlot: TBD Business Sector: Mining 
DGS Minerals previously traded on the TSX Venture Exchange. 
If you have any questions or require further information, please contact Listings at (416) 367-7340 or E-mail: Listings@thecse.com .
